Quickstrike:





Quickstrike ducked his head, slowly getting his temper under control. He 
knew getting mad at Stingtra for no reason wasn't going to help. He had to 
be patient on a matter like this.

He paused and watched his scanners. He found Stingtra's signature and saw 
that she was back at base. He felt like an idiot now, just trying to chase 
her tail. He growled at himself and made his way back.

When he came back, he barely saw anyone, even when he said for no one to 
leave. Dark Mouse and Megatron wasn't here either. But he did see Stingtra 
hurting herself again. He ran over to her and knelt down. He blocked her 
head before she hit it again over the wall of the cave.

"This is what ah'm talkin' about," he said, watching carefully with his 
temper.
